    <ThingDef ParentName="GW_HOI_ArmorBase">
        <defName>GW_HOI_CadianCommanderArmor</defName>
        <label>Cadian castellan armor</label>
        <description>Light, durable, and sporting the distinct markings, to don the Castellan Armor is to take on the responsibilities of command. While few commanders enter the battlefield, the Castellan is always prepared to take up arms and lead from the front.</description>
